snippet.title: STRAY | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
STRAY is coming to PS5 and PC in 2021. Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1332010/Stray/

Lost, alone, and separated from family, a stray cat must untangle an ancient mystery to escape a long-forgotten cybercity and find the way home.

Developed by BLUETWELVE. Published by Annapurna Interactive. 

© Annapurna Interactive, 2020
